NAME: E621
AUTHOR: Alzarath
DESCRIPTION:
Search https://e621.net/ for furry pictures.

Usage: [p]e621 [tags...]: Fetch the latest image
[p]e621r [tags...]: Fetch a random image
[p]e621filter list: Lists all filters applied to the server
[p]e621filter add [filter name]: Add a filter to the server
[p]e621filter del [filter name]: Delete a filter from the server

Disclaimer: By default this cog does not display NSFW content, but it is able to through setting filters.
